üß† Interpretation Framework
¬†¬†¬†‚Ä¢¬†¬†¬†Œ≤ > 0.1 ‚Üí cooperative (amplifies stability)
¬†¬†¬†‚Ä¢¬†¬†¬†Œ≤ < ‚Äì0.1 ‚Üí antagonistic (cross-cancel)
¬†¬†¬†‚Ä¢¬†¬†¬†|Œ≤| ‚âà 0 ‚Üí neutral (independent)
¬†¬†¬†‚Ä¢¬†¬†¬†Optimum point from GAM = predicted maximum system coherence.
