üî¥ Chaotic	high œÉ, low Œ¶‚Çõ	overload; governance drift or crisis brewing
üîµ Rigid	low œÉ, low Œ¶‚Çõ	stagnation; ossified or complacent state

Color gradient (red ‚Üí yellow ‚Üí green) visualizes institutional vitality.

