This is the Tessrax Federation Reflex:
¬†¬†¬†‚Ä¢¬†¬†¬†Autonomic control kept one system alive.
¬†¬†¬†‚Ä¢¬†¬†¬†Distributed control keeps a civilization of agents alive.
