üß¨ Behavior

Metric	Role	Interpretation
Entropy (·π†)	surprise rate	high ‚Üí instability; low ‚Üí stagnation
Scar Flux (Œ¶scar)	healing rate	high ‚Üí reconciliation in progress
Reflex (œà‚ÇÄ)	rhythm coherence	high ‚Üí synchronized governance
Composite œà	metabolic signal	directs breathing speed

Cadence compresses when entropy spikes; stretches when scar flux surges (system healing).
This creates a dynamic breathing pattern across the network‚Äîoscillating between vigilance and rest.

‚∏ª

