This closes Tessrax‚Äôs metabolic loop:
	1.	Sensing: Coherence, entropy, scars.
	2.	Integration: Weighted neural-like summation.
	3.	Action: Adjust governance cadence and audit rhythm.
	4.	Feedback: Effects logged ‚Üí new sensing data.

Entropy and scar flux now counterbalance like heat and repair. The network doesn‚Äôt just stabilize; it lives within bounded turbulence.

