When |R‚àí1| > Œ¥ for Œît > œÑ/4:
    invoke adaptive_update()
    broadcast new {C, Q} to federated nodes
    record œá(t) to coherence ledger

This turns the static governance kernel into a living organism‚Äîaudits accelerate when entropy spikes, then slow once the system stabilizes.

‚∏ª

7. Resulting Behavior
¬†¬†¬†‚Ä¢¬†¬†¬†Self-healing: spikes in entropy accelerate decision cadence until scars close.
¬†¬†¬†‚Ä¢¬†¬†¬†Anti-lock reflex: noise and covariance logging prevent phase-locked loops.
¬†¬†¬†‚Ä¢¬†¬†¬†Continuous adaptation: the federation evolves rhythmically toward stability.

